-[id="llm-proxy-future-logging_{context}"]
-== Planned audit logging capabilities
-
-Red{nbsp}Hat plans to provide the following audit logging capabilities:
-
-* Structured JSON log events per completed LLM transaction, including request routing, response latency, and token count metadata.
-* User-to-request correlation by using anonymized user identifiers.
-* Forwarding structured log streams to a SIEM system (such as Splunk or Elasticsearch) by using the Red{nbsp}Hat OpenShift Logging Operator.
